Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.04,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was only a small wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.97,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Everyday life where nothing happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:12.04,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,each day gently continuing on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.08,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,During those days which were more dear than anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.85,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,a shadow silently descended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:21.38,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The power to sever the chain that is destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:24.36,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If it could be granted to these hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.79,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I would not mind throwing everything else away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.57,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Our oath under the stars of the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:34.56,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,With the sword in this hand, to set forth the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:40.07,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's{\i1} will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:51.68,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Prayers echoing in the vast skies turn to miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:14.64,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Teardrops melt and flow into the blue of the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:20.82,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I met a warmth that engulfs all without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.85,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Just like the pure white snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.92,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Words that are honest no matter how far you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:33.80,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It moves me as I wear wings of steel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:39.33,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Each time I am hurt,\NI can become kinder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:47.77,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,My only wish is to protect that smile of yours to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:54.82,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Memories of sadness engraved across the ages
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:02:01.16,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,You are an angel of light, catching them straight on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:06.96,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,An eternal blaze that stopped in my heart that day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.43,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Releasing the deep darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:16.80,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It opens the door of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:23.73,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Towards the strong, boundless future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:35.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,An artificial lifeform that isn't a familiar or a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:37.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that something like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:43.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate, you just had a slightly different way of being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:47.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You are a human who was properly granted life into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The test results said so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Stop talking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to explain on the monitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The guardians are programs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:10.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,embedded within the Book of Darkness taking on human forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Book of Darkness is reincarnated, reborn over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but these four, together with the Book of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:19.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,have been through many masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Enough conversational skills to maintain consistency
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:25.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,have been confirmed in past cases as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:28.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but there's never been a case where they have shown any emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Collection for the Book of Darkness and their master's guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That is their only objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But that girl in the hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita was acting angry and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I felt a clear personality from Signum as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That she had something she needed to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That it was for her comrades and her mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,For her mistress, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Concerning that, let's wait for information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,from the agents who are investigating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Looking at their frequency of teleports,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:07.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,there's no doubt that their master is somewhere in this vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It just may be the case that we'll be able to catch the master first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be great, because it's easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's before the Book of\NDarkness is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,she should be an ordinary mage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:23.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'd like more detailed data about the Book of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask something of you, starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.73,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.33,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,What kind of a person do you think the Book of Darkness's mistress is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:45.50,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The Book of Darkness randomly chooses someone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.44,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,with potential to control it as its new host.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.77,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.54,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,You never know.\NMaybe she's someone our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.11,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Of all things, I think that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.79,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Suzuka has a friend sleeping over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.83,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.26,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.30,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.30,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Hayate Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.30,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,She said she'll introduce us next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.39,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:25.53,Nanoha A's Title1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur0.5\frx-30\pos(476,615)}It Was Only a Small Wish\N(part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well then, thanks a lot, Suzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:36.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please, please do come again, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:49.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate says she will be back shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is Vita still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Apparently she's gone pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She said she'll be back by evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What about you, Signum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:03.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:09.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your magical powers seem to be quite drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your leader was not made to be that weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:14.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You have changed quite a bit too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:22.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You never laughed like that in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Was that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,All of us have changed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:34.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all from the day that\NHayate became our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If you're together with relatives, it must be very good and merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:48.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's like every day is needlessly fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's already been over six months since everyone came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.52,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(476,576)}Anfang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.52,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Start up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Confirmed startup of the Book of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We are the guardian knights
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,who will gather for the Book of\NDarkness and protect its mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Clouds that gather under the Mistress of the Night Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Wolkenritter{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.48,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(505,650)}Cloud Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please, your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita, shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:32.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Stay quiet. Discourtesy in front of your mistress is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Discourtesy, or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:37.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,she looks like she's passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:38.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:43.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad nothing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We really were surprised by what happened back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What kind of people are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though it's spring, it's still cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:14.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and they brought you in without even putting on a jacket, Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They're dressed so strangely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and I don't understand what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They're all so suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:24.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, um, how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.89,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If you give us an order, we can be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.58,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,What would you have us do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:36.89,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It's telepathy. If you can wish for a command in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.96,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's more like a favor to ask than a command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.90,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Play along with what\NI'm going to say, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.94,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, Dr. Ishida,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,actually, those people are my relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:54.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They came by to wish me a happy birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:59.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,from their distant home countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:03.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And they tried to surprise me, and dressed up in costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I got too surprised by all of this, and....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:10.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it goes... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Just as she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.96,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Our new mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.11,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Mistress Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Her young age was one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.54,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but she differed in many ways from our previous masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So this is what you call the Book of Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:39.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's been on the bookshelf as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.45,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I took good care of it because it was a very pretty book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At the time of awakening, and while you were asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,did you hear the voice of the Book of Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:54.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not a mage or anything, so everything's kind of vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's one thing that I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,As the mistress of the Book of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,clothing, food, and shelter for all the guardian knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:06.05,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I have to look after all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:09.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I have a place to live, and I'm good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy clothes for all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so let me measure you and figure out your size.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.19,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yes... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.82,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Everything was different from all our previous masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:26.57,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Mistress Hayate's treatment of us, unlike our other masters,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:30.56,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,wasn't beating down on us or treating us like tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:34.64,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was as if she were treating us like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's ready! Let's all eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll have some to eat now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll have some to eat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.64,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,We had our hesitations...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:09.65,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,However, as our new mistress wished,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.64,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,we were starting to live a quiet everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Seconds, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Knight Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:37.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We possess weapons, but we must be given armor by our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We can make them with our own magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so if you could think up images of their forms...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:48.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to make you fight or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How about clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:51.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Clothes that look like knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Yes, that would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then I have to look things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I have to think up really cool-looking ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.61,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\b1\c&H00FF00&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs56\pos(196.133,392)\shad5.0\4a&64&}Toys 'R' Oos{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:01.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Places like this have materials of the sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:06.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Vita?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:14.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This is a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The perfect day to go on a stroll!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.30,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You can take it out of the bag now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate, than...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.39,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Time passed by so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.86,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,We, together with our mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.30,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,had been spending our lives with nothing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Wow, so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:56.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Mistress Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is it really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,About the Book of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,As soon as you wish it so,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:09.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,we can fill the pages of the Book of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and you can gain great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your legs would heal as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,To fill the pages of the Book of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:22.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,you have to trouble all sorts of people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's wrong to trouble other people for your own selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:35.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm plenty happy as I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom are up in the skies already,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:43.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but my uncle is keeping tabs on the inheritance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:47.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,One of your father's friends, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:51.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him, I don't face any troubles in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:55.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Besides, more than anything else, right now I have all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's up, Vita?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:11.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate, can I eat the ice cream in the freezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:15.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You ate that much dinner, yet you're going to eat more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:18.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm on a growth spurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate's meals are giga-delicious, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:24.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum, you're their leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your current master, Hayate Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,wishes nothing from the Book of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:46.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,As long as I am your master, forget about the Book of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:50.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your job is to live all together, happily in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:59.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I so pledge, on my sword as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Life... in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate's legs, for some unknown reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,suffer from a nerve-based paralysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:21.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In the past six months, the paralysis has slowly moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Especially in the past two months...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At this rate, there is the danger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.96,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that her internal organs will become paralyzed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:34.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Why didn't we notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Mistress Hayate's condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was not an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The curse of the Book of Darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:57.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Book of Darkness, with Mistress\NHayate ever since she was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,was closely linked to our mistress' body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The strong magical powers that have been suppressed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:08.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,ate away at our mistress' body, as she had a young Linker Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Getting in the way not only of healthy physical activity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but threatening basic operations for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:21.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And when our mistress met her first awakening, that sped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That meant our mistress was using her magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,though only a very tiny amount,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,to sustain the activities of the four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:37.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly claim to have had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We have to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:45.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We have to save Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Shamal! Shamal, you're good at the healing stuff, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,An illness like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,My powers cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We can do so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.27,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It is the curse of the Book of Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.14,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,that is eating away at our mistress' body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.14,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If Hayate were to truly awaken
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.98,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,as the mistress of the Book of Darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:30.25,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Our mistress' illness would fade away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.35,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,At the least, it would stop progressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:36.05,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tarnish Hayate's future with blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.02,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,so I won't kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,But I won't stop at anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.10,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry, mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:50.40,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Just this once, we will break the vow we have made to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:14.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us for this wrongdoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.74,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Everyone, they look so good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.43,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Time for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:41.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You completely trashed the knight's outfit Hayate gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, the clothes will heal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:50.27,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and I got a decent amount of pages, so I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,...doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,...hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Something like this doesn't hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:07.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's different from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When I get home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:18.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that I have a warm bath—and Hayate's food—waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:23.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Kind Hayate is waiting for me with a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:29.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:39.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Something like this doesn't hurt one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:57.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The three of us came together, but is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:01.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, we left Allex to do the monitoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.94,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We just have to investigate the Book of Darkness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:04.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The two we're about to meet are in the know for that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The Liese....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. It's me, Chrono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chroboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Wow, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.23,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're being so cold to the trainers you haven't seen in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Aria! Do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:34.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, so let her do what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Besides, well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's not that you hate it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Of course that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:43.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:45.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Liesearia, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:46.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Lieselotte is as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Do something about this, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:51.29,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, despite being my twin,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,there's no accounting for some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Lieselotte, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:06.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's a tasty-looking little mouse-boy here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.27,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:15.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Why is someone like that my trainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:21.35,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're searching for the Book of Darkness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:23.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I heard the situation from Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:26.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll be as much help as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:31.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They're the trainers who taught\NChrono magic and melee combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:39.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Liesearia, in charge of magical training,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:42.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and Lieselotte, in charge of melee combat training.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:46.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They are twin familiars of Admiral Graham,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:48.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and as you can tell, their base form is a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:52.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:54.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It would be really reassuring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:57.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,if the two of you could come out to the outpost,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:59.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but you have jobs right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:03.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We still have to teach a few new armed agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:07.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So we can't stay over on your end for too long. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:12.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No, actually, what I wanted to ask of you was about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:15.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Can I eat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:16.11,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:18.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When you're done with everything, do what you want with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:25.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So, what's your request?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:31.01,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I would like you to help him in his research in the Infinity Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:41.59,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I won't forget even when I grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:49.52,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the day that we came across each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:54.30,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,In this place, where flowers bloom intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:58.01,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I kept you in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:01.41,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I remember the promise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:07.87,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the smile that I love so much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:18.52,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,That day, when the secret door opened
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:25.96,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I was chasing after a small white butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:34.21,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I got lost, and I wanted to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.21,0:24:37.95,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My true wishes, my true feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:42.45,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Maybe you taught those to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.45,0:24:46.59,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Guarded by such kind feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:50.16,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I was spoiled for all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.16,0:24:53.96,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,How you thought dear of me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.96,0:24:59.93,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, I won't forget all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.56,0:25:11.76,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Yuuno's research,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.76,0:25:13.17,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,the truth of the Book of Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.17,0:25:14.87,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,is becoming clearer and clearer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.87,0:25:17.84,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,How my serious duel with\NSignum will turn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:21.07,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,And that masked man shows up again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.98,0:25:25.05,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Next episode of\N{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's:{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.05,0:25:28.55,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Episode 7: With the Broken Past and Present
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.48,0:25:31.64,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Drive Ignition!
